;general html element attributes, including widgets, e.g. `$macrocall`
:» `<$widget attribute=<<variable>>/>`
:» `<$widget attribute=<<callMacroToComputeValue>>/>`
:» `<$widget attribute={{transclusion}}/>`
:» @@.warn ~~`<$widget attribute="prefix-<<variable>>"/>`~~@@
:» @@.warn ~~`<$widget attribute=[[prefix-<<variable>>]]/>`~~@@
